Type: Package
Package: hamsteR
Title: Conditional source function
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Marc O. Rüdel <mor@uni-bremen.de>
Maintainer: Marc O. Rüdel <mor@uni-bremen.de>
Description: This package provides a conditional 'source'
    function.  HamsteR can remembers which files have already been loaded
    (and parsed) and can prevent reloading. You can specify which files
    have been successfully loaded and which must be reloaded.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Depends:
    R (>= 3.5)
Imports: 
    base,
    tools (>= 3.5),
    utils (>= 3.5)
Suggests: 
    spelling (>= 2.1),
    testthat (>= 2.1.0),
    covr (>= 3.3.2),
    devtools (>= 2.2.1),
    roxygen2 (>= 6.1.1)
Encoding: UTF-8
Language: en-US
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
